properties.name: Aunt Lyn and Uncle Bill
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereLyn and Bill live in Austin, TX. When we visit them we eat in awesom Mexican restaurants, row, shop, and buy cowboy boots! I love visiting with them because Laura, my cousin, and I go hiking.

properties.name: Aunt Mary
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereAunt Mary is from Pennslyvania. When we visit my family loves to spend the day on the lake. But because she lives so far away, I don\'t get to see her a lot. She is the mom of my cousins Pat and Jack.

properties.name: Cousin Jack
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereCousin Jack is a famous chef in Miami. Whenever I go to visit him he always cooks me the most delicous meals and always remembers to take me to the beach,

properties.name: Grandma and Grandpa
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereI always go fishing and pick pecans from trees when I visit my Grandma and Grandpa. They live in Great Falls, SC which is in the middle of nowhere so there is a lot of relaxing whenever I go to visit them.

properties.name: Grandmother LaVonne
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereLaVonne as I call her is my grandmother, She lives down the street from my parents in Chattanooga. She grows day lillies and has tons of dogs. She is kind of crazy but I like to visit her because she has the biggest rocks in her yard to boulder.

properties.name: Granny Nanny and Papa Jolley
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereGranny Nanny and Papa Jolley live in a beautiful condo on the river right across from the art district, I live to visit them and watch the view.

properties.name: Parents
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereSo my family resides on Signal Mtn, TN. Whenever I visit them, I spend the whole time relaxing. When it\'s summer I spend all my freetime jet skiing. I love going home and visiting my dogs.

properties.name: Pat and Jack
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywherePat and Jack are my cousins. They live in Kentucky together and Pat is getting married and expecting soon. Whenever I visit them we spend all day chilling and watching tv.

properties.name: Uncle Charles
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereUncle Charles is in the military and lives in Virginia. Whenever my family visits, we spend all day on the lake or play nintendo with his daughter Amy.

properties.name: Uncle Sam
properties.description: Posted by CjolleywhereUncle Sam lives in San Francisco, CA. Whenever we visit him we go to Chinatown. He also takes us to exotic grocery stores.
